F1 Ranking is a chrome extension designed to provide Formula One racing enthusiasts with up-to-date information about the latest and historical standings. This extension is a useful add-on that helps you stay informed about the latest developments in the F1 world.

By clicking "Add to Chrome", I accept and agree to installing the Chrome extension and setting Chrome New Tab to that provided by the service. The search features within the extension will be provided by Microsoft Bing.
